#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
AlJeel AP Pipeline v25 — Family-booking folder discovery + PC-family emp_no fix

Three targeted fixes over v24:

  FIX A — Adjacent-ticket folder expansion (deterministic)
    For a family booking folder named "6904732429 family", the existing discovery
    only finds it for ticket 6904732429. Tickets 6904732430 / 6904732431 fall back to
    surname matching and pick up unrelated folders (e.g. "6904687314" for HUSSEIN,
    "05apr/train ticket 2" for SALEM). v25 expands the reverse index so that any folder
    (a) named "<10-digit> family" or (b) containing a PC email is also indexed under
    adjacent ticket numbers ±1..5.  Dedicated folders (exact match) take priority.

  FIX B — PC email filename → structured LLM context
    The .msg filename already encodes the responsible employee: e.g.
    "...Personal Contribution Approval Requested for Mahmoud Elkilany Hussein (1002466)..."
    v25 pre-extracts this (emp_no + name) from the PC index and injects it as a strong
    prior into the classify/resolve LLM prompt, so the model doesn't have to parse it from
    the email body.  This benefits both the employee's own ticket AND family-member tickets.

  FIX C — PC-family dependent emp_no rule (deterministic post-processing)
    Truth convention for AlJeel: when a personal-contribution booking (account=21070229)
    is for a FAMILY MEMBER of the responsible employee (not the employee themselves),
    emp_no should be blank ("") while the CC/GL allocation still comes from the
    employee's master record.
    Detection: after all resolution, for any row with account=21070229, if the
    passenger's first name (from "LASTNAME/FIRSTNAME" format) does NOT appear in the
    PC-email employee's full name → blank emp_no.

Root causes fixed (J26-550):
  HUSSEIN/TALIA (CHD)  6904732429 — right folder ✅ but emp_no=1002466 not blank → Fix C
  HUSSEIN/YOUSSEF MR   6904732430 — wrong folder (6904687314) → wrong CC → Fix A + Fix C
  SALEM/EFFAT MRS      6904732431 — wrong folder (train ticket 2) → wrong CC → Fix A + Fix C

Usage:
    python3 scripts/run_v25.py J26-550                          # primary fix target
    python3 scripts/run_v25.py J26-640                          # golden regression check
    python3 scripts/run_v25.py J26-593                          # blind regression check
    python3 scripts/run_v25.py J26-589
    python3 scripts/run_v25.py J26-788 --input-suffix v15.11.2
    python3 scripts/run_v25.py J26-550 --limit 15 --skip-fraud  # smoke test rows 1-15
"""
